  #pragma once
  
  #include "click.h"
  
  namespace click {
  
    typedef shared_ptr<Plustache::Context> CONTEXT;
    typedef durian::generator<durian::XmlElement::Body> XMLBODY;
    typedef PlustacheTypes::CollectionType COLLECTION;
    typedef PlustacheTypes::ObjectType MAP;
  
    namespace enhance {
      namespace dataManagement {
  
        namespace Element {
          
          struct Attribute {
            string AttributeCaption;
            string AttributeDataType;
            string AttributeReferenceType;
            string AttributeValueIdentifier;
            string AttributeValue;
            Attribute(string _AttributeCaption, string _AttributeDataType, string _AttributeReferenceType, string _AttributeValueIdentifier, string _AttributeValue) : 
              AttributeCaption(_AttributeCaption), AttributeDataType(_AttributeDataType), AttributeReferenceType(_AttributeReferenceType), AttributeValueIdentifier(_AttributeValueIdentifier), AttributeValue(_AttributeValue) {};
          };
  
          struct AttributeMember {
            string AttributeMemberCaption;
            string AttributeMemberDataType;
            string AttributeMemberValueIdentifier;
            COLLECTION collection;
            vector<string> AttributeMemberCollection;
            AttributeMember(string _AttributeMemberCaption, string _AttributeMemberDataType, string _AttributeMemberValueIdentifier, vector<string> _AttributeMemberCollection) :
              AttributeMemberCaption(_AttributeMemberCaption), AttributeMemberDataType(_AttributeMemberDataType), AttributeMemberValueIdentifier(_AttributeMemberValueIdentifier), AttributeMemberCollection(_AttributeMemberCollection) {
              for (const auto& e : AttributeMemberCollection) { collection.emplace_back(MAP{ { "Value", e } }); }
            }
            AttributeMember(string _AttributeMemberCaption, string _AttributeMemberDataType, string _AttributeMemberValueIdentifier, COLLECTION _collection) :
              AttributeMemberCaption(_AttributeMemberCaption), AttributeMemberDataType(_AttributeMemberDataType), AttributeMemberValueIdentifier(_AttributeMemberValueIdentifier), collection(_collection) {}
          };
  
          struct WebService {
            string WebServiceName;
            string WebServiceID;
            string WebServiceValue;
            string WebServiceTypeName;
            COLLECTION collection;
            vector<string> Attributes;
            WebService(string _WebServiceName, string _WebServiceID, string _WebServiceValue, string _WebServiceTypeName) :
              WebServiceName(_WebServiceName), WebServiceID(_WebServiceID), WebServiceValue(_WebServiceValue), WebServiceTypeName(_WebServiceTypeName) {}
            WebService(string _WebServiceName, string _WebServiceID, string _WebServiceValue, string _WebServiceTypeName, vector<string> _Attributes) :
              WebServiceName(_WebServiceName), WebServiceID(_WebServiceID), WebServiceValue(_WebServiceValue), WebServiceTypeName(_WebServiceTypeName), Attributes(_Attributes) {
              for (const auto& e : Attributes) { collection.emplace_back(MAP{ { "value", e } }); }
            }          
          };
  
          struct WebServiceRoot {
            string webService;
            WebServiceRoot(string _webService) : webService(_webService) {}
          };
        }      
  
        class helper {
        public:
          
          string createElement(Element::Attribute el) {
            CONTEXT ctx = make_shared<Plustache::Context>();
  
            ctx->add("AttributeCaption", el.AttributeCaption);
            ctx->add("AttributeDataType", el.AttributeDataType);
            ctx->add("AttributeReferenceType", el.AttributeReferenceType);
            ctx->add("AttributeValueIdentifier", el.AttributeValueIdentifier);
            ctx->add("AttributeValue", el.AttributeValue);

Get template and compile with your context

 
            string tplPath = "tpl/click/dataManagementServices/Attribute";
            XMLBODY body;
            auto requestXmlString = body.compile(ctx, tplPath);
  
            return *requestXmlString;
          }
  
          string createElement(Element::AttributeMember el) {
            CONTEXT ctx = make_shared<Plustache::Context>();
  
            ctx->add("AttributeMemberCaption", el.AttributeMemberCaption);
            ctx->add("AttributeMemberDataType", el.AttributeMemberDataType);
            ctx->add("AttributeMemberValueIdentifier", el.AttributeMemberValueIdentifier);
            ctx->add("AttributeMember", el.collection);

            string tplPath = "tpl/click/dataManagementServices/AttributeMember";
            XMLBODY body;
            auto requestXmlString = body.compile(ctx, tplPath);
  
            return *requestXmlString;
          }
  
          string createElement(Element::WebService el) {
            CONTEXT ctx = make_shared<Plustache::Context>();
  
            ctx->add("WebServiceName", el.WebServiceName);
            ctx->add("WebServiceID", el.WebServiceID);
            ctx->add("WebServiceValue", el.WebServiceValue);
            ctx->add("WebServiceTypeName", el.WebServiceTypeName);

            XMLBODY body;

            Element::WebServiceRoot webServiceRoot{ *ws };
